{"title":"Must Watch: Steve Peat takes Claudio to the Limit in Retro Trails","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/12/must-watch-steve-peat-takes-claudio-to-the-limit-in-retro-trails/","date":1626101992000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Take Claudio to the Limit is a new five part series challenging World Cup Downhill legend Claudio Caluori to crazy riding-related challenges on the trails of Graubuenden, Switzerland. Steve Peat, another star of downhill, is the first to Take Claudio to the Limit. The challenge? A “race” down the exposed ridge lines of Davos aboard a retro Klunker hand picked by Gary Fisher, feat. lycra and speed traps.</p><h2>Retro Trail: Take Claudio to the Limit</h2><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7z2knexhIT0?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.6195692374626254\"></iframe></span></p><p>French enduro racer Morgane Such, German slopestyle and YouTube hero Lukas Knopf, French downhill superstar Loic Bruni and Danish endurance specialist Annika Langvad are up next, with their own special challenges designed to Take Claudio to the Limit.&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/12105603/claudio-caluori-races-klunker-davos-switzerland-steve-peat-retro-trails.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/12105603/claudio-caluori-races-klunker-davos-switzerland-steve-peat-retro-trails.jpg\" alt=\"claudio caluori klunker racing switzerland steve peat\" width=\"1200\" height=\"799\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/12105603/claudio-caluori-races-klunker-dav